        <h2>Allrecipes Magazine Recipe Testing</h2>
        <blockquote>Recipes selected for publication in Allrecipes magazine get further scrutiny and testing.. Magazine recipes are tested one to four times in our test kitchens in Des Moines, Iowa, and Birmingham, Alabama.</blockquote>
